      "outbounds": [
          {
              "protocol": "freedom",
              "settings": {}
          }
      ]
  }
  ```
- **Edit the Configuration File:** Replace `"your_vmess_id"` with your actual V2Ray ID and adjust settings as needed.

**c. Start V2Ray:**
- Open the V2Ray GUI or command line interface to start the service.

